constraints.ocl:
context Tag
inv: self.posts->size() >= 1 and self.posts->size() <= 1

context Conversation
inv: self.messages->size() >= 2 and self.messages->size() <= 2

context FriendRequest
inv: self.createdAt <> '' and self.createdAt.size() > 0

context Group
inv: self.memberships->notEmpty() implies self.memberships->last().joinedAt <> null

context Tag
inv: self.posts->notEmpty() implies self.posts->sortedBy(x | x.content)->first().content <= self.posts->sortedBy(x | x.content)->last().content

context Conversation
inv: self.createdAt.size() >= 5 implies self.createdAt.substring(1, 5) = 'value'

context Post
inv: self.comments->notEmpty() implies self.comments->last().text <> null

context Post
inv: self.media->notEmpty() implies self.media->sortedBy(x | x.url)->first().url <= self.media->sortedBy(x | x.url)->last().url

context Group
inv: self.memberships->forAll(x, y | x <> y implies x.joinedAt <> y.joinedAt)

context User
inv: self.posts->forAll(x, y | x <> y implies x.isPublic <> y.isPublic)

context Conversation
inv: self.participants->size() >= 2 implies self.participants->asSequence()->at(2).email <> null

context Post
inv: (self.reactions->size() >= 1 and self.reactions->size() <= 3) and (self.reactions->size() < 1)

context User
inv: not(self.username <> null implies self.email <> null)
